# Fast gate before pushing: lint + typecheck + integration tests. All quick,
# deterministic, and need no browser or running dev server. The heavy Playwright
# e2e + a11y suite is intentionally NOT here — CI runs it on every PR
# (.github/workflows/ci.yml), so duplicating it locally only adds minutes and
# flakiness. Run it on demand with `npm run test:e2e` when you touch those flows.
npm run lint
npm run typecheck
npm run test:int
